<body>
<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 5: 200 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.1">季康子問于孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.2">"肥從有司之後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.3">一不知民務之安哉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.4">唯子之賜憂."</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.5">請問</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.6">君子之從事者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-1a.7">於民之 [1]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.2 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 5: 202 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-2a.1">[孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-2a.2">仁之以]德,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-2a.3">此君子大務也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-2a.4">康子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-2a.5">請問何謂仁之以德?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.3 (STRIPS 2-3) MACHENGYUAN 5: 202, 204 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a.2">君子在民[2]之上,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a.3">執民之中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a.4">施教於百姓,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a.5">而民不服焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-3a.6">是君子之恥也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.4 (STRIPS 3-4) MACHENGYUAN 5: 204, 206 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.1">是故君子玉其言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.2">而成其行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.3">敬成其[3]德以臨民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.4">民望其道而服焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.5">此之謂仁之以德.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.6">且管仲有言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.7">君子恭則遂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.8">驕則侮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-4a.9">備言多難 [...][4]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.5 (STRIPS 11, 18, 6) MACHENGYUAN 5: 219, 227, 211 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.1">[...] 矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.2">康子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.3">毋乃肥之聞也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.4">是差乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.5">固如吾子之足肥也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.6">孔子[11] 辭曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.7">子之言也, 已重.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.8">丘也聞君子 [18] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.9">[康子曰:]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-5a.10">寧移肥也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.6 (STRIPS 6, 7) MACHENGYUAN 5: 211, 212 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.2">丘聞之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.3">孟子餘曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.4">“夫書者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.5">以著君子之德也 [6].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.6">夫詩也者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.7">以誌君子之志.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.8">夫儀者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.9">以謹君子之行也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.10">君子涉之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.11">小人觀之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.12">君子敬成其德,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-6a.13">小人晦眛. [7]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.7 (STRIPS 5, 22B) MACHENGYUAN 5: 210, 233 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.1">面事皆得其喚</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.2">而強之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.3">則邦有奸動.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.4">百姓送之以 [...] [5]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.5">滅速毋恒哉!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.6">後之世比亂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.7">邦相懷毀,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.8">眾必惡善.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-7a.9">賢人 [...] [22B]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.8 (STRIPS 11A, 18B) MACHENGYUAN 5: 219, 227 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.1">深厚.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.2">是故夫迫邦甚難,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.3">民能易移 [...] [11A]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.4">田肥,民</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.5">則安.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.6">瘠,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.7">民不樹.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.8">是故賢人大於邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.9">而有厚心,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-8a.10">能為畏[...] [18B]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.9 (STRIPS 17, 12) MACHENGYUAN 5: 226, 220 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.1">[...] 者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.2">因古典禮</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.3">而彰之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.4">毋逆百事,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.5">皆請行之. [...] [17]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.6">[...] 安焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.7">作而乘之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-9a.8">則邦有穫.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.10 (STRIPS 12, 15B, NEILI APP) MACHENGYUAN 5: 220, 223, MACHENGYUAN 4: 229 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.1">先之所善,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.2">亦善之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.3">先之所事[12]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.4">[...] 惡毋事;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.5">先人 之所廢,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.6">毋起.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.7">然則民降不善,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.8">靡父兄子弟而稱讎 [15B]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-10a.9">[...] 無難.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.11 (STRIPS NEILI APP, 8) MACHENGYUAN 4: 229, MACHENGYUAN 5: 214 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-11a.1">毋忘姑姐妹</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-11a.2">而遠敬之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-11a.3">則民有禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-11a.4">然後奉之以中庸 [...] [內禮 SM4.6 appended strip]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-11a.5">[...] 也縈.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.12 (STRIPS 8, 21) MACHENGYUAN 5: 214, 232 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.1">烈今語肥也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.2">以處邦家之術曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.3">君子不可以不強,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.4">不強則不立. [8]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.5">[...] [君子不可以不]威,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.6">[不]威則民然 (?) 之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.7">[...] 毋信玄憎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.8">毋信玄憎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.9">因邦之所賢</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-12a.10">而舉之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.13 (STRIPS 21, 22A, 22B) MACHENGYUAN 5:232, 233, TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.1">大罪殺 [21] 之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.2">常罪刑之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.3">少罪罰之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.4">苟能固守[22A]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.5">而行之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.6">民必服矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-13a.7">故子以此言為奚如?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.14 (STRIPS 22B, 14, 15) MACHENGYUAN 5: 233, 223, 223 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.2">"由丘觀之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.3">則美[22B]言也已.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.4">且夫, 烈今之先人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.5">世三代之傳史,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.6">豈敢不以其先人之傳志告?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.7">康子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.8">然其囑人亦曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-14a.9">古之[14]為邦之必以此.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.15 (STRIPS 15, 9, 10) MACHENGYUAN 5: 223, 215, 216 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.2">"言則美矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.3">然 [15] 異於丘之所聞.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.4">丘聞之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.5">藏文仲有言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.6">“君子強則遺,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.7">威則民不導 [9],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.8">滷則失眾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.9">礧則亡親,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.10">好刑則不祥,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-15a.11">好殺則作亂.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.16 (STRIPS 10, 19) MACHENGYUAN 5: 216, 228 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.1">是故賢人之居邦家也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.2">夙興夜寐, [10]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.3">降端以比,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.4">民之勸美,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.5">弃惡毋歸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.6">慎小以合大,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-16a.7">疏言而密守之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIKANGZIWEN 5.23.17 (STRIPS 19, 20) MACHENGYUAN 5: 228, 230 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.1">毋欽遠,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.2">毋詣逐,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.3">惡人勿陷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.4">好[19]人勿貴,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.5">救民以親,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.6">大罪則處之以刑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.7">常罪則處之以罰,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0052_tls_001-17a.8">少罪訿之.</seg>
                </p>

